Yes, LoS very important.  In the case when another mob pops when the first one dies be very careful with archery. (City of Mist and Plane of Sky are two good examples.)  Especially if the objective is to NOT kill the second mob right away or at all.  You could have an arrow in the air as the first one dies that will then hit the second.  So put away the arrows when the mob is low health in these situations.<br>
<br>
