<br>
Keep your &quot;jolt&quot; spell memmed so your healer doesn't have to waste mana healing you over and over. Let the main tank take the damage no matter how satisfying it might be to steal aggro from him <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br>
<br>
Watch your group members' health. You might be able to land a small heal on one of them while the cleric is casting Complete Heal and save their life. <br>
<br>
Use harmony if needed to help with crowd control. I have used harmony in Hate to help the puller single pull Maestro. It is also useful in CoM to clear out the throne room in an organized manner before entering. Heh, I've seen a ranger pull in Hate. Interesting to watch (translation: glad it wasn't me) <p>Prismata Banestalker<br>
